### Cities
GET {{host}}/api/cities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Districts (Łódź)
GET {{host}}/api/cities/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111/districts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reverse geocode
POST {{host}}/api/buildings/reverse-geocode
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lat": 51.7592,
  "lon": 19.4560
}

### Notes
GET {{host}}/api/notes?cityId=11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111&level=City
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
